1. A whale address that opened a PEPE position a week ago sold 1 trillion PEPE and made a profit of more than 3.5 million US dollars;
2. Trader Eugene: Bitcoin may hit a record high, and altcoins are expected to rebound strongly;
3. Crypto KOL Edgy: After the official account of Cointelegraph was stolen, a private message was sent to it in an attempt to steal the X account;
4. TRUMP official: 3.5 million TRUMPs were deposited in CEX to enhance liquidity, and reiterated that all previously unlocked tokens have been locked;
5. A whale address withdrew 4 million USDC from Binance to purchase nearly 300,000 TRUMPs.
